{"tid":1600074,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【反送中MV】留守於今天 擔起這個責任 不甘香港給予送贈！","createTime":"2019-09-28T12:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T12:37:48.000Z","uid":309931,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"757168a5b0fbed721984bb16c9b08141f852d445","tid":1600074,"uid":309931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=g8E0obko-BY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg8E0obko-BY&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=25ced262\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=g8E0obko-BY</a><br />\n<br />\n原：落花流水 陳奕迅<br />\n作詞：黃偉文<br />\n作曲：Eric Kwok/陳奕迅<br />\n編曲：Eric Kwok/Jerald Chan<br />\n<br />\n詞:白衣天弑<br />\n唱:Sunny 晴天林<br />\n<br />\n歌詞在下：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人鏈 在獅子山上發光嗎<br />\n維園 共結百萬人出發<br />\n便覺得這裏正是我家<br />\n從前靜土以遭風化 漸喪一朵 亡花<br />\n<br />\n相遇 在煲底下去抗爭嗎<br />\n心願 便化做連儂抒發<br />\n每字 鏗鏘編寫出 渴望自由<br />\n立志 不撤 不散<br />\n<br />\n留守於今天 擔起這個責任<br />\n不甘香港給予送贈<br />\n這尚旅途未怕艱辛<br />\n亦是無負這一生<br />\n幾多 欺壓拒做賤民<br />\n一起 守護自由聲音<br />\n熱淚都流過 記心頭怒憤<br />\n（氣餒低沉過 逆境中抗爭）<br />\n<br />\n文宣 讓小島內遍佈開花<br />\n民居 共約定十時呼喊<br />\n為了家 征戰拒絕折返<br />\n沿途儘管 滿遭險壓 未信可以 回家<br />\n<br />\n思念 在天空上見證的他<br />\n堅毅 讓故事劇程轉化<br />\n要是 撿起把雨遮 各自上爬<br />\n暴雨侵淹 開傘<br />\n<br />\n高呼聲 怎都不散 匯聚大街小鎮 集結全城人去佈陣<br />\n雞蛋 憾牆無懼 誰被殺<br />\n造夢時 不區分<br />\n<br />\n餘生於香港 只得這個責任<br />\n真的身份堅拒送贈<br />\n槍雨彈林未怕犧牲<br />\n為着時代拼一生<br />\n催煙 槍炮抹掉淚痕<br />\n堅守 公義毋忘初心<br />\n但願都捱過戰爭 來互吻<br />\n或是寫下了 歷史留烙印<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n感謝晴天巴唱咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n運動走到100多日又係雨革5週年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望呢首歌可以畀啲鼓勵大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10月1日再集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用大家嘅力量留下歷史嘅烙印！！！"},{"pid":"8f05c24b4ce6ed4b5e35c38bfcb4eefdb919c983","tid":1600074,"uid":309931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T12:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DfrnKhK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDfrnKhK.jpg&h=9c786ab4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3caf86d17982de9cca70d2565732b68c4ef7c53","tid":1600074,"uid":309931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T12:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PZNaTdX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZNaTdX.jpg&h=3edb1ded&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"335700822695cb95c8362dc40eed50cea4f65549","tid":1600074,"uid":309931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T12:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ibOEUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ibOEUD.jpg&h=02fab4b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LbfjUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LbfjUF.jpg&h=4c67668c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ci6KXGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fci6KXGn.jpg&h=f748d928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNkf4mo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNkf4mo.jpg&h=58479630&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"611f3f5f23ea0ad6760f64afe6b1969cf11bdc40","tid":1600074,"uid":309931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T12:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ibOEUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ibOEUD.jpg&h=02fab4b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LbfjUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-s